# ====================================================================
# MTF analytics — root .gitignore
#
# Strategy:
#  • Raw reports (mtf_reports/) are committed — per project policy.
#  • Derived files served to the dashboard (mtf_daily_totals*.{json,csv},
#    compressed_data/*.json.gz) are committed.
#  • Heavy intermediates (stock_analytics.json), backups, run logs,
#    Python build artifacts, editor/OS cruft, and local virtualenvs
#    are ignored.
# ====================================================================

# --- Heavy intermediates regenerated by the pipeline (~1.7 GB) ----
# extract_stock_data.py writes this; compress_stock_data.py consumes it.
# Never commit — far too big and changes every run.
stock_analytics.json
stock_analytics_compressed.json.gz

# --- NSE equity master cache (symbol → ISIN) ----
# Re-fetched every pipeline run from nsearchives.nseindia.com; checked-in
# version would go stale and confuse readers.
mtf_reports/NSE/_equity_master.csv

# --- Live market caps (ISIN → mcap_lakhs) ----
# fetch_market_caps.py pulls this fresh from BSE's ListofScripData
# endpoint every CI run; extract_stock_data.py consumes it to enrich the
# Market Changes feed. Regenerated each run — never committed (changes
# daily, would churn history).
/market_caps.json

# --- Compressed stock chunks (~38 MB / refresh) ----
# Rebuilt fresh in CI every cron run and uploaded directly to Cloudflare Pages
# via `wrangler pages deploy` (no git push needed). Keeping them out of git
# avoids bloating history by ~38 MB per refresh.
compressed_data/
mtf_dashboard_v4/compressed_data/*.json.gz
mtf_dashboard_v4/compressed_data/manifest.json

# --- Derived daily-totals files (regenerated by extract_daily_totals_complete_fix.py
# + sanitize_daily_totals.py) ----
# Generated fresh by CI every run, sync'd into mtf_dashboard_v4/ before
# `wrangler pages deploy`, never committed. Kept on local disk so dev work
# doesn't have to regenerate from raw reports every time.
/mtf_daily_totals.json
/mtf_daily_totals.csv
/mtf_daily_totals_complete.json
/mtf_daily_totals_complete.csv
/mtf_daily_totals_crores.json
/mtf_daily_totals_crores.csv
/mtf_daily_totals_complete_crores.csv
mtf_dashboard_v4/mtf_daily_totals.json

# --- AUM-by-class composition split ----
# Root copy is a build intermediate (regenerated by extract_stock_data.py).
# The deployed copy mtf_dashboard_v4/mtf_aum_by_class.json IS committed: unlike
# daily totals, this file is produced by the cache-gated stock extraction, so a
# UI-only redeploy (cache hit) skips its regeneration and needs the tracked copy.
/mtf_aum_by_class.json

# --- Run logs ----
*.log
*.log.*

# --- Backups produced by sanitize/trim scripts ----
*.bak
*.pre-trim.bak

# --- Scratch / debugging artifacts ----
# I prefix all temp scripts and screenshots with an underscore.
_*.py
_*.html
_*.png
_*.txt
/tmp/
/temp/

# --- Python ----
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
build/
dist/
pip-wheel-metadata/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# --- Virtual environments ----
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
.python-version

# --- Node / wrangler (we use them via npx in CI; nothing should land in git) ----
node_modules/
.wrangler/
.cloudflare/

# --- Editor / IDE ----
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.cursorignore
.aider*
.history/

# --- Claude Code local settings ----
# `.local.json` is a user-local override per Claude Code's convention.
# Permission allowlists and other personal config don't belong in git.
.claude/settings.local.json

# --- OS cruft ----
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- Headless Chrome test profiles ----
chrome-profile-*/
.chromium-profile/

# --- Legacy dashboard folders (v4 is the only active deploy target) ----
mtf_dashboard_v3/
mtf_dashboard_final/
mtf_dashboard_production/

# --- Legacy prototype HTMLs at repo root (index_v2.html is the active dev source — keep) ---
/index.html
/index1.html
/index_simple.html
/mtf_dashboard.html
/mtf_advanced_dashboard.html
/test_dashboard.html

# --- Legacy single-deploy Cloudflare Pages config at repo root (v4 has its own) ---
/wrangler.toml
/_headers
/_redirects

# --- Old archive snapshots ----
/mtf.zip
/mtfs.zip
/mtfed.zip
/mtfer.zip
/mtfing.zip
/mtfly.zip

# --- Old notes / one-off debug data ----
/BSE_MTF_Data_Structure_Analysis.md
/ENHANCED_FEATURES_SUMMARY.md
/omsprop-specific_message_replacement.txt
/missing_dates.txt
/slb.csv
/mtf_trends_visualization.png
